query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS exchange_feature_categories (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  slug VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  nameZh VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL,
  nameEn VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL,
  icon VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  descZh TEXT NOT NULL,
  descEn TEXT NOT NULL,
  difficulty ENUM('beginner','intermediate','advanced') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'beginner',
  sortOrder INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS exchange_feature_support (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  exchangeSlug VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  featureSlug VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  supported BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT TRUE,
  levelZh VARCHAR(128),
  levelEn VARCHAR(128),
  detailZh TEXT,
  detailEn TEXT,
  maxLeverage VARCHAR(32),
  feeInfo VARCHAR(256),
  highlight BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  UNIQUE KEY uq_exchange_feature (exchangeSlug, featureSlug)
);
